txt.en: 'No, that is not the password. And what do you mean by that? I would say anyone wandering around is either lost or up to no good, like one o' them Rangers. I saw a Ranger in town up by the Pony yesterday morn, and he gave me a look such as I've never earned, I'll tell you that much. Seems to me we'd be better off if them Rangers went a-wandering and got themselves good and lost!\n\n'But that's not the password!'
Not All Who Wander Are Lost.
